This directory has domain descriptions for two blocks
world demos.  "blocks.pddl" is the standard blocks world
in hierarchical task network form (what AP does best).
"multi-agent.pddl" is a variation demonstrating AP's ability
to coordinate multiple agents.

PDDL documentation can be found here:
ftp://ftp.cs.yale.edu/pub/mcdermott/software/pddl.tar.gz

